        <updateDate>2011-01-13T18:04:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fair Sentencing Clarification Act of 2010 - Provides for the retroactive application of the penalty&nbsp;amendments of the Fair Sentencing Act of 2010 to cocaine base offenses committed prior to the enactment of such Act.&nbsp;Authorizes a court to reduce the term of imprisonment consistent with the amendments made by such Act for a person convicted of&nbsp; the crime of possession of a substance which contains cocaine base committed before August 3, 2010.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
